WEBVTT

NOTE
Testimonial by Veggie Fada — Agribiz Africa / Qualiseed Pay Small Small scheme

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
My name is Veggie Fada, and I'm a farmer in Ghana.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:14.000
With the Pay Small Small plan from Agribiz Africa and Qualiseed,
I was able to get quality seeds and fertilizers without a big upfront cost.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:22.000
I just pay in small installments as I go —
it has made farming much easier for me.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Now I can grow more, earn more,
and I don't have to worry about not having enough money to start.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:38.000
I encourage every farmer to take advantage of this opportunity.
Agribiz Africa and Qualiseed are truly supporting us.
